        "action": "Make it compulsory for websites to state if product packaging is recyclable.",
        "additional_details": "Society is becoming increasingly conscious about our environmental impact and sustainable living.\r\n\r\nLook at your average supermarket online shopping websites. The majority of these sites do not have any information about whether their product\u2019s packaging is recyclable.\r\n\r\nLook at any cosmetic brands where you can purchase online, these also lack the same information.",
        "background": "With the growth of online shopping and with the current crisis surrounding sustainable materials. Companies should clearly state on their product pages whether the product is sustainably sourced or easily recycled. The modern day consumer would like to know if what they are purchasing,is sustainable",
